{{Documentation subpage}}
{{High-use}}
<!-- Please place categories where indicated at the bottom of this page and interwikis at Wikidata (see [[Wikipedia:Wikidata]]) -->

== Usage ==
All available parameters:
* {{para|genus}}
* {{para|species}}
* {{para|access-date}} or {{para|accessdate}}
* {{para|date}}
* {{para|year}}

;Example

The code:<syntaxhighlight lang=wiki>
{{NRDB species|genus=Eunectes|species=beniensis|date=12 December|year=2008}}
</syntaxhighlight>
: outputs:
::{{NRDB species|genus=Eunectes|species=beniensis|date=12 December|year=2008}}

== See also ==
* [[Template:NRDB family]]
* [[Template:NRDB genus]]
* [[:Commons:Template:ReptileDB species]]

<includeonly>{{sandbox other||
<!-- Categories below this line, please; interwikis at Wikidata -->
[[Category:Snake templates]]
[[Category:Biology external link templates]]
}}</includeonly>

